&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Analyze performance and optimize campaigns&lt;/strong&gt; by monitoring key lifecycle metrics such as engagement, retention, and lifetime value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate with Revenue Operations&lt;/strong&gt; to ensure clean data pipelines, robust data enrichment, and seamless integrations that maximize lifecycle marketing potential.&lt;/li&gt;
